query:
SELECT u.id, u.email, u.name, u.role, u.organizationId, o.name as orgName, om.role as memberRole
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN organizations o ON u.organizationId = o.id
LEFT JOIN organizationMembers om ON u.id = om.userId AND u.organizationId = om.organizationId
WHERE u.email LIKE '%proagentur%' OR u.email LIKE '%niaghi%'
LIMIT 10;
